<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
Magic Block Puzzle respects your privacy. This policy explains how information is handled when you use the app.
</p>

<h2>Information Collection</h2>
<p>
Magic Block Puzzle does not require account creation, login, or registration.
We do not directly collect, store, or share personal information.
</p>

<h2>Gameplay Data</h2>
<p>
The app may store game-related data such as scores locally on your device.
This data is used only to improve your gameplay experience and is not transmitted to us.
</p>

<h2>Advertising</h2>
<p>
Magic Block Puzzle displays advertisements provided by third-party advertising services.
These services may collect certain information, such as device identifiers,
to show relevant ads in accordance with their own privacy policies.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>
The app may use third-party services (such as advertising SDKs)
that may collect information used to identify your device.
We do not control how these third parties handle your data.
</p>

<h2>Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h2>
<p>
Magic Block Puzzle does not knowingly collect personal information from children.
Advertisements, if shown, are served by third-party providers in compliance with applicable laws.
</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>
This privacy policy may be updated from time to time.
Any changes will be posted on this page.
</p>

